{"type":"answer","id":238710,"parentType":"question","parentId":23448,"uid":27926,"contents":"<center>\"<b>Real power begins where secrecy begins.</b>\"</center><br>\n<center>———Hannah Arendt, <i>The Origins of Totalitarianism</i>, Chapter XII</center><br>\n<center>https://www.atlasofplaces.com/essays/the-origins-of-totalitarianism/</center><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/gdJlnmf.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/gdJlnmf.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/gdJlnmf.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n在極權國家，保密工作宣傳如同給玩具上發條，每過一段時間就要來一次以維持機器的運轉。<br>\n至於哪些是密，什麽是涉密標準，則不可問不可説——説了就錯，問了就會被打。<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/1C9rgb4.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/1C9rgb4.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/1C9rgb4.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/rlECxGD.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/rlECxGD.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/rlECxGD.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/orhySfF.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/orhySfF.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/orhySfF.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/RfLRfNb.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/RfLRfNb.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/RfLRfNb.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<s>P.S. 話説，品蔥上台灣人很多噠，中國人小心被控泄密哦：）——企鵝文共賞《小心！台谍就在你身边！》https://new.qq.com/omn/20180916/20180916A0B9MX.html</s>","date":"2020-04-13","agreeCount":4,"discussionCount":0}